{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_24021.jpg","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":4.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21173.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21171.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"fade"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21012.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102003,"motion":300,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21012.jpg","nameNarration":"","narration":"*Knock knock*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21012.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Good morning, Miss Satori."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102003,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Oh...Miss Nurse."},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"You're being discharged today.@Congratulations!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102003,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah... Thank you very much."},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'll leave your breakfast here, then..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_21012.jpg","chara":[{"id":102003,"pos":1},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800600}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Door closes*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21012.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102003,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Phew... Right, I'm being discharged."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":102003,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(In the afternoon, I'll visit Crescent House,)"},{"chara":[{"id":102003,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(and greet everyone...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102003,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102003,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"I think I'll leave the hospital a little early@and go to the library..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...@...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Why...am I...)"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(only looking up things about Miss Jeanne?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Miss Jeanne as in Jeanne d'Arc?>"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<It almost sounds like you know her personally?>"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(...I need to be quiet in the library.)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"white","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:After the death of Jeanne d'Arc,@the Kingdom of France, under the leadership@of Marshal Richemont, continued military@reforms and achieved victory after victory@against England. In 1453, the Hundred Years'@War effectively came to an end.]","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narration":"[textBlack:King Charles VII became known@as the \"Victorious King\".]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:In 1449, Charles VII recaptured@the town of Rouen, where Jeanne@had been condemned as a heretic.@The following year, he ordered@a re-examination of the@legitimacy of her trial.]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:Subsequently, a retrial took@place, and on July 7, 1456,@the Church declared her@previous heresy trial@invalid.]"},{"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830200}],"narration":"[textBlack:The judgment that had labeled Jeanne a@heretic was torn apart and discarded.@Jeanne's former comrades, her mother Romée,@and the citizens of Orléans that she had saved,@all rejoiced.]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402800,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narration":"[textBlack:Jeanne's legend continued to@be cherished and passed down.@After hundreds of years,@on May 6, 1920, Jeanne d'Arc@was canonized by the Pope@and officially recognized@as a \"saint\".]"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Charles VII... He really kept his promise...!)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(The feelings of Jeanne La Pucelle were properly@passed down...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...@..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(...What promise was that...?)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"white","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:In 1440, a rebellion known as the@\"Praguerie\" occurred, led by@nobles supporting the coronation@of Dauphin Louis. However,@it was quickly suppressed when@Dauphin Louis surrendered.]","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"[textBlack:As a result, Charles VII's military@reforms made significant progress,@and France advanced rapidly@towards the elimination of@England's influence and the@restoration of domestic@security.]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:Dauphin Louis later ascended@the throne as King Louis XI@of France.]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:Throughout his life, he continued@to express gratitude to@Jeanne d'Arc and is known to@have named his two daughters@\"Jeanne\" in her honor.]"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(I don't know why it caught my attention, but...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(I feel somehow relieved...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Um, this section...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Alchemist Nicolas Flamel and his wife Perenelle@Flamel...?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Ah...! I should be leaving soon."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"I'll be late for my get-together..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
